add_ac

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_ac -  Adds a default ac to the npc for when they fight unarmed.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_ac(string ac_name,
string ac_type,
mixed ac_amount)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ac_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the ac
%^BOLD%^ac_type%^RESET%^ - the type of the ac
%^BOLD%^ac_amount%^RESET%^ - the damage/roll stuff to take off
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/races/base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Adds a default ac to the npc for when they fight unarmed.  Please look
add the armour object for more details on this.
.EP

